    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of parts. The engine currently runs very roughly and will likely require a complete overhaul or replacement to be roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows significant signs of age, including noticeable rust spots, faded paint, and several dents. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electrical components. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it to its new home.",
