    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smooth and shifts well, with a consistent service history that suggests many more miles of reliable driving ahead. It\u2019s a great choice for someone who wants a dependable, attractive car without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
