      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant. This unit maintains factory-spec vacuum routing and an unmolested wiring harness. Recent compression testing confirms strong, symmetrical pulses across all rotor faces. The kinematics are preserved via original double-wishbone suspension and pristine bushings, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains communicative. Power is transferred through a crisp five-speed manual to a Torsen limited-slip differential. Finished in Montego Blue, the exterior retains its factory luster, while the cockpit shows zero UV-induced thermal degradation. A rare, turnkey specimen of JDM engineering precision.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Flawless exterior. Garage kept. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
